images.accessibilityLabel: Our annual Gecko Fest is held each year on the Saturday of Labor Day weekend.  It's a fun and colorful event that attracts thousands to the Village.  GeckoFest is the finale of a full month of whimsical Gecko-themed events, including the annual Art Gecko Show, Gecko Pub Crawl and Gecko Ball, celebrating the end of summer and Gulfport's unofficial mascot and favorite reptile!
